data.description: CUTE home located on a quiet cul-de-sac. This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home has beautiful wood flooring & tile throughout. The first of two living rooms has a cozy wood burning fire place with built in bookshelves on each side. The second spacious living area runs into the formal dining area were you'll also find the beautiful hardwood flooring carried through. The kitchen has sparkling granite counter tops & stainless steel appliances. This home also features a sun room perfect for a game area!!
